description:
Checkpoint of a deep neural network model for DTM generation, made in the context of the project available on github : https://github.com/davpergan/DTM_DSM_GAN/. 

 The model is an adapted version of the pix2pix model (https://www.tensorflow.org/tutorials/generative/pix2pix?hl=en), trained with a modified loss function, using the gradient and normal criteria from 

 &quot;Amini Amirkolaee, Hamed et al. &ldquo;DTM Extraction from DSM Using a Multi-Scale DTM Fusion Strategy Based on Deep Learning.&rdquo;  Remote sensing of environment  274 (2022): 113014&ndash;. Web.&quot;

